      "type": "action",
      "tool": "edit",
      "code": "{\"filePath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\README.md\", \"oldString\": \"**Tech stack (prototype only):**\\n\\n| Layer | Choice | Why |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| UI framework | React 19 + TypeScript | Type-safe components that mirror Frappe shapes |\\n| Router | TanStack Router / TanStack Start | File-based routing, SSR-ready |\\n| Server | Nitro (via `@lovable.dev/vite-tanstack-config`) | Thin SSR wrapper, Cloudflare-ready |\\n| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 + shadcn/ui (Radix primitives) | Rapid design-system iteration |\\n| State / data | In-memory mock store (`src/mock-data/`) | No backend needed for prototype |\\n| Query | TanStack Query v5 | Mirrors how real Frappe data will be fetched |\\n| Dev tooling | Bun, Vite 8, ESLint, Prettier | Fast iteration |\", \"newString\": \"**Tech stack (prototype only):**\\n\\n| Layer | Choice | Why |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| UI framework | Vue 3 + TypeScript | Type-safe components that mirror Frappe shapes |\\n| Router | Vue Router 4 | File-based routing, SSR-ready |\\n| Server | Vite 8 | Fast HMR, production build |\\n| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 + frappe-ui | Rapid design-system iteration, Frappe design tokens |\\n| State / data | In-memory mock store (`src/mock-data/`) | No backend needed for prototype |\\n| Dev tooling | Node.js, Vite 8, ESLint, Prettier | Fast iteration |\"}",
