      "code": "{\"filePath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\README.md\", \"newString\": \"| Route | File | Key components | Frappe target |\\n|---|---|---|---|\\n| `/` | `views/HomeView.vue` | PostCard, SentimentBadge | `GP Discussion` list |\\n| `/spaces/:spaceId` | `views/SpaceView.vue` | PostCard, NewPostModal | `GP Project` + `GP Discussion` filtered |\\n| `/posts/:postId` | `views/PostDetailView.vue` | Comment thread, reactions, similar posts | `GP Discussion`, `GP Comment`, `GP Reaction` |\\n| `/events` | `views/EventsView.vue` | Event card grid, RSVP button | `FG Event`, `FG Event Attendee` |\\n| `/mentors` | `views/MentorsView.vue` | Match request, match card | `FG Mentor Match` |\\n| `/courses` | `views/CoursesView.vue` | Course card grid | `LMS Course` |\\n| `/courses/:courseId` | `views/CourseDetailView.vue` | Chapter list, lesson list, enrol | `LMS Course`, `LMS Chapter`, `LMS Enrollment` |\\n| `/courses/:courseId/lessons/:lessonId` | `views/LessonView.vue` | Lesson player, YouTube embed, progress | `LMS Lesson`, `LMS Course Progress` |\\n| `/members` | `views/MembersView.vue` | Filterable directory | `User` + `GP User Profile` |\\n| `/members/:userId` | `views/MemberDetailView.vue` | Profile card, posts, badges | `GP User Profile` |\\n| `/messages` | `views/MessagesView.vue` | Thread list | `Raven Channel` |\\n| `/messages/:threadId` | `views/ThreadView.vue` | Message bubbles, send form | `Raven Message` |\\n| `/notifications` | `views/NotificationsView.vue` | Notification inbox | `Notification Log` |\\n| `/settings` | `views/SettingsView.vue` | Notifications, Privacy, Integrations, AI, SSO | `FG User Settings`, `FG AI Settings`, `Social Login Key` |\\n| `/docs` | `views/DocsView.vue` | In-app documentation panel | \\u2014 |\", \"oldString\": \"| Route | File | Key components | Frappe target |\\n|---|---|---|---|\\n| `/` | `routes/index.tsx` | PostCard, SentimentBadge | `GP Discussion` list |\\n| `/spaces/:spaceId` | `routes/spaces.$spaceId.tsx` | PostCard, NewPostModal | `GP Project` + `GP Discussion` filtered |\\n| `/posts/:postId` | `routes/posts.$postId.tsx` | Comment thread, reactions, similar posts | `GP Discussion`, `GP Comment`, `GP Reaction` |\\n| `/events` | `routes/events.tsx` | Event card grid, RSVP button | `FG Event`, `FG Event Attendee` |\\n| `/mentors` | `routes/mentors.tsx` | Match request, match card | `FG Mentor Match` |\\n| `/courses` | `routes/courses.tsx` | Course card grid | `LMS Course` |\\n| `/courses/:courseId` | `routes/courses.$courseId.tsx` | Chapter list, lesson list, enrol | `LMS Course`, `LMS Chapter`, `LMS Enrollment` |\\n| `/courses/:courseId/lessons/:lessonId` | `routes/courses.$courseId.lessons.$lessonId.tsx` | Lesson player, YouTube embed, progress | `LMS Lesson`, `LMS Course Progress` |\\n| `/members` | `routes/members.tsx` | Filterable directory | `User` + `GP User Profile` |\\n| `/members/:userId` | `routes/members.$userId.tsx` | Profile card, posts, badges | `GP User Profile` |\\n| `/messages` | `routes/messages.tsx` | Thread list | `Raven Channel` |\\n| `/messages/:threadId` | `routes/messages.$threadId.tsx` | Message bubbles, send form | `Raven Message` |\\n| `/notifications` | `routes/notifications.tsx` | Notification inbox | `Notification Log` |\\n| `/settings` | `routes/settings.tsx` | Notifications, Privacy, Integrations, AI, SSO | `FG User Settings`, `FG AI Settings`, `Social Login Key` |\\n| `/docs` | `routes/docs.tsx` | In-app documentation panel | \\u2014 |\"}",
