      "code": "{\"description\": \"Read all Vue views\", \"prompt\": \"Read ALL of these Vue view files in full and return the complete contents of each one. I need to see every line of code. The files are:\\n\\n1. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\HomeView.vue\\n2. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\EventsView.vue\\n3. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\MembersView.vue\\n4. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\MemberDetailView.vue\\n5. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\CoursesView.vue\\n6. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\CourseDetailView.vue\\n7. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\CourseNewView.vue\\n8. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\LessonView.vue\\n9. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\MentorsView.vue\\n10. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\MessagesView.vue\\n11. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\ThreadView.vue\\n12. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\NotificationsView.vue\\n13. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\PostDetailView.vue\\n14. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\SpaceView.vue\\n15. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\SettingsView.vue\\n16. C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\community-launchpad-proto\\\\src\\\\views\\\\DocsView.vue\\n\\nReturn the COMPLETE contents of each file.\", \"subagent_type\": \"general\"}",
      "output": "<task id=\"ses_11ba4dfcbffe3W3WOgHi0304Ak\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\nHere are the complete contents of all 16 Vue view files:\n\n---\n\n### 1. `HomeView.vue` (39 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout>\n    <div class=\"max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6\">\n      <header class=\"mb-5\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-[24px] font-bold leading-tight\">Home</h1>\n        <p class=\"text-[14px] text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">Latest from across your Spaces.</p>\n      </header>\n\n      <div\n        class=\"mb-4 rounded-xl bg-primary-soft/60 border border-primary-soft p-3 flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[13px] text-primary-soft-foreground\"\n      >\n        <span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0\">✨</span>\n        <div>\n          <strong>UX prototype.</strong> Clickable design demo built with in-memory mock data.\n          Schema matches the real\n          <code class=\"font-mono text-[12px] bg-card/60 px-1 rounded\">frappe/lms</code>\n          +\n          <code class=\"font-mono text-[12px] bg-card/60 px-1 rounded\">frappe/gameplan</code>\n          DocTypes. See\n          <RouterLink to=\"/docs\" class=\"underline underline-offset-2\">/docs</RouterLink>.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div data-tour=\"feed\" class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n        <PostCard v-for=\"p in posts\" :key=\"p.id\" :post=\"p\" />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </AppLayout>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { computed } from \"vue\";\nimport { RouterLink } from \"vue-router\";\nimport AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\nimport PostCard from \"@/components/PostCard.vue\";\nimport { getDiscussions } from \"@/data/store\";\n\nconst posts = computed(() => getDiscussions());\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. `EventsView.vue` (107 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout>\n    <div class=\"max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6\">\n      <header class=\"mb-5\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-[24px] font-bold leading-tight\">Events</h1>\n        <p class=\"text-[14px] text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">\n          Show up, meet people, ask questions. RSVPs are casual.\n        </p>\n      </header>\n\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n        <article\n          v-for=\"e in events\"\n          :key=\"e.id\"\n          class=\"rounded-xl bg-card border border-border p-5 flex gap-4 hover:border-border-strong transition-colors\"\n        >\n          <div\n            class=\"size-14 rounded-lg bg-secondary flex flex-col items-center justify-center shrink-0\"\n          >\n            <div class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">\n              {{ getMonth(e.starts_on) }}\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"text-[20px] font-bold leading-none\">{{ getDay(e.starts_on) }}</div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[12px] text-muted-foreground mb-1\">\n              <span\n                class=\"px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground font-medium\"\n                >{{ e.event_type }}</span\n              >\n              <template v-if=\"getProject(e.space)\">\n                <span>·</span>\n                <span>{{ getProject(e.space)?.icon }} {{ getProject(e.space)?.title }}</span>\n              </template>\n            </div>\n            <h2 class=\"text-[16px] font-semibold leading-snug\">{{ e.title }}</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-[13px] text-muted-foreground mt-1 line-clamp-2\">{{ e.description }}</p>\n\n            <div class=\"mt-2 flex flex-col gap-1 text-[12px] text-muted-foreground\">\n              <div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5\">🕐 {{ formatDate(e.starts_on) }}</div>\n              <div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                <template v-if=\"e.location_type === 'In Person'\"\n                  >📍 {{ e.physical_address }}</template\n                >\n                <template v-else-if=\"e.location_type === 'Online (BigBlueButton)'\"\n                  >📹 BigBlueButton · {{ e.bbb_meeting_id }}</template\n                >\n                <template v-else>🔗 {{ e.external_link }}</template>\n              </div>\n              <div v-if=\"getUser(e.hosted_by)\" class=\"text-muted-foreground\">\n                Hosted by {{ getUser(e.hosted_by)?.full_name }}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"mt-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n              <span class=\"text-[12px] text-muted-foreground\"\n                >{{ goingCount(e.id) }}/{{ e.capacity }} going</span\n              >\n              <div class=\"flex gap-1\">\n                <button\n                  v-for=\"s in ['Going', 'Maybe', 'Not Going'] as const\"\n                  :key=\"s\"\n                  class=\"text-[12px] h-7 px-3 rounded-full border transition-colors\"\n                  :class=\"\n                    getMyRSVP(e.id) === s\n                      ? 'bg-primary text-primary-foreground border-primary'\n                      : 'border-border text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary'\n                  \"\n                  @click=\"setRSVP(e.id, s)\"\n                >\n                  {{ s }}\n                </button>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </AppLayout>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { computed } from \"vue\";\nimport AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\nimport { getEvents, getAttendees, getMyRSVP, getProject, getUser, setRSVP } from \"@/data/store\";\nimport type { RSVPStatus } from \"@/mock-data/types\";\n\nconst events = computed(() => getEvents());\n\nfunction getMonth(iso: string) {\n  return new Date(iso).toLocaleString(undefined, { month: \"short\" }).toUpperCase();\n}\nfunction getDay(iso: string) {\n  return new Date(iso).getDate();\n}\nfunction formatDate(iso: string) {\n  return new Date(iso).toLocaleString(undefined, {\n    weekday: \"short\",\n    hour: \"numeric\",\n    minute: \"2-digit\",\n  });\n}\nfunction goingCount(eventId: string) {\n  return getAttendees(eventId).filter((a) => a.rsvp_status === \"Going\").length;\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. `MembersView.vue` (34 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout>\n    <div class=\"max-w-[920px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6\">\n      <header class=\"mb-5\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-[24px] font-bold leading-tight\">Members</h1>\n        <p class=\"text-[14px] text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">Connect with other FirstGens.</p>\n      </header>\n\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n        <RouterLink\n          v-for=\"u in members\"\n          :key=\"u.user\"\n          :to=\"`/members/${u.user}`\"\n          class=\"rounded-xl bg-card border border-border p-5 flex flex-col items-center text-center hover:border-border-strong transition-colors\"\n        >\n          <AppAvatar :user-id=\"u.user\" :size=\"56\" />\n          <div class=\"mt-3 text-[14px] font-semibold\">{{ u.full_name }}</div>\n          <p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-muted-foreground line-clamp-2\">{{ u.bio }}</p>\n          <div class=\"mt-2 text-[11px] text-primary font-semibold\">View profile →</div>\n        </RouterLink>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </AppLayout>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { computed } from \"vue\";\nimport { RouterLink } from \"vue-router\";\nimport AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\nimport AppAvatar from \"@/components/AppAvatar.vue\";\nimport { getUsers } from \"@/data/store\";\n\nconst members = computed(() => getUsers());\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. `MemberDetailView.vue` (71 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout>\n    <div class=\"max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6\">\n      <div v-if=\"!u\" class=\"p-12 text-center\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-[18px] font-semibold mb-2\">Member not found</h2>\n        <RouterLink to=\"/\" class=\"text-primary underline\">Back home</RouterLink>\n      </div>\n      <template v-else>\n        <div\n          class=\"h-28 rounded-xl\"\n          :style=\"{\n            background: `linear-gradient(135deg, ${u.image_background_color}, var(--secondary))`,\n          }\"\n        />\n        <div class=\"flex items-end gap-4 -mt-10 px-4 mb-5\">\n          <div class=\"rounded-full bg-card p-1\">\n            <AppAvatar :user-id=\"u.user\" :size=\"72\" />\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"pb-1 flex-1\">\n            <h1 class=\"text-[20px] font-bold leading-tight\">{{ u.full_name }}</h1>\n            <p class=\"text-[13px] text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">{{ u.bio }}</p>\n          </div>\n          <button\n            v-if=\"!isMe\"\n            type=\"button\"\n            class=\"h-9 px-3 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-[13px] font-semibold inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:opacity-90\"\n            @click=\"messageMember\"\n          >\n            💬 Message\n          </button>\n        </div>\n\n        <section>\n          <h2 class=\"text-[14px] font-semibold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">\n            Recent posts\n          </h2>\n          <div\n            v-if=\"posts.length === 0\"\n            class=\"text-[13px] text-muted-foreground py-8 text-center border border-dashed border-border rounded-xl\"\n          >\n            No posts yet.\n          </div>\n          <div v-else class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n            <PostCard v-for=\"p in posts\" :key=\"p.id\" :post=\"p\" />\n          </div>\n        </section>\n      </template>\n    </div>\n  </AppLayout>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { computed } from \"vue\";\nimport { RouterLink, useRoute, useRouter } from \"vue-router\";\nimport AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\nimport AppAvatar from \"@/components/AppAvatar.vue\";\nimport PostCard from \"@/components/PostCard.vue\";\nimport { getUser, getRecentPostsByUser, openOrCreateDMWith, currentUserId } from \"@/data/store\";\n\nconst route = useRoute();\nconst router = useRouter();\nconst userId = computed(() => route.params.userId as string);\nconst u = computed(() => getUser(userId.value));\nconst posts = computed(() => getRecentPostsByUser(userId.value));\nconst isMe = computed(() => userId.value === currentUserId);\n\nfunction messageMember() {\n  const t = openOrCreateDMWith(userId.value);\n  router.push(`/messages/${t.id}`);\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. `CoursesView.vue` (74 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout>\n    <div class=\"max-w-[1040px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-5 gap-4 flex-wrap\">\n        <div>\n          <h1 class=\"text-[24px] font-bold leading-tight\">Courses</h1>\n          <p class=\"text-[14px] text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">\n            Bite-sized, self-paced. Take what's useful, skip what isn't.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <RouterLink\n          to=\"/courses/new\"\n          class=\"h-9 px-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-[13px] font-semibold inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:opacity-90\"\n        >\n          + Create course\n        </RouterLink>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n        <RouterLink\n          v-for=\"c in courses\"\n          :key=\"c.id\"\n          :to=\"`/courses/${c.id}`\"\n          class=\"group rounded-xl bg-card border border-border p-5 flex flex-col hover:border-border-strong transition-colors\"\n        >\n          <div\n            class=\"aspect-video rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-soft to-secondary mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-4xl\"\n          >\n            📘\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] text-muted-foreground mb-1\">\n            <span class=\"font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider\">{{ c.category }}</span>\n            <span v-if=\"c.featured\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-0.5 text-flag-foreground\"\n              >⭐ Featured</span\n            >\n            <span\n              v-if=\"getEnrollment(c.id)\"\n              class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-0.5 text-primary-soft-foreground\"\n              >✓ Enrolled</span\n            >\n          </div>\n          <h2 class=\"text-[15px] font-semibold leading-snug group-hover:text-primary\">\n            {{ c.title }}\n          </h2>\n          <p class=\"text-[13px] text-muted-foreground mt-1 flex-1\">{{ c.short_introduction }}</p>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-3 text-[12px] text-muted-foreground\">\n            <span>📖 {{ c.lessons }} lessons</span>\n            <span>👤 {{ c.enrollments }}</span>\n          </div>\n          <div v-if=\"getEnrollment(c.id)\" class=\"mt-3\">\n            <div class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary overflow-hidden\">\n              <div\n                class=\"h-full bg-primary transition-all\"\n                :style=\"{ width: `${courseProgressPercent(c.id)}%` }\"\n              />\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"text-[11px] text-muted-foreground mt-1\">\n              {{ courseProgressPercent(c.id) }}% complete\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </RouterLink>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </AppLayout>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { computed } from \"vue\";\nimport { RouterLink } from \"vue-router\";\nimport AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\nimport { getCourses, getEnrollment, courseProgressPercent } from \"@/data/store\";\n\nconst courses = computed(() => getCourses());\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 6. `CourseDetailView.vue` (226 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout>\n    <div class=\"max-w-[900px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6\">\n      <div v-if=\"!course\" class=\"p-12 text-center\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-[18px] font-semibold mb-2\">Course not found</h2>\n        <RouterLink to=\"/courses\" class=\"text-primary underline\">Back to courses</RouterLink>\n      </div>\n      <template v-else>\n        <!-- Hero -->\n        <div class=\"rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-border bg-card mb-5\">\n          <div\n            class=\"aspect-[4/1] bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-soft via-secondary to-primary-soft flex items-center justify-center text-6xl\"\n          >\n            📘\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"p-6\">\n            <div class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold text-muted-foreground\">\n              {{ course.category }}\n            </div>\n            <h1 class=\"text-[26px] font-bold leading-tight mt-1\">{{ course.title }}</h1>\n            <p class=\"text-[15px] text-secondary-foreground mt-2\">{{ course.description }}</p>\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mt-4 text-[13px] text-muted-foreground flex-wrap\">\n              <span\n                >By\n                <RouterLink\n                  :to=\"`/members/${course.author}`\"\n                  class=\"text-foreground font-semibold hover:underline\"\n                  >{{ getUser(course.author)?.full_name }}</RouterLink\n                ></span\n              >\n              <span>📖 {{ course.lessons }} lessons</span>\n              <span>👤 {{ course.enrollments }} enrolled</span>\n              <span v-if=\"course.enable_certification\" class=\"text-primary-soft-foreground\"\n                >🏆 Certificate on completion</span\n              >\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap\">\n              <template v-if=\"enr\">\n                <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-[180px]\">\n                  <div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-secondary overflow-hidden\">\n                    <div class=\"h-full bg-primary transition-all\" :style=\"{ width: `${pct}%` }\" />\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"text-[12px] text-muted-foreground mt-1\">{{ pct }}% complete</div>\n                </div>\n                <button\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  class=\"h-10 px-5 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-[14px] font-semibold inline-flex items-center gap-2 hover:opacity-90\"\n                  @click=\"goToFirst\"\n                >\n                  ▶ Continue\n                </button>\n              </template>\n              <button\n                v-else\n                type=\"button\"\n                class=\"h-10 px-5 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-[14px] font-semibold hover:opacity-90\"\n                @click=\"enrollInCourse(courseId)\"\n              >\n                Enroll for free\n              </button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Chapters -->\n        <section>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-[16px] font-semibold\">Course content</h2>\n            <button\n              v-if=\"isAuthor\"\n              type=\"button\"\n              class=\"h-8 px-3 rounded-full border border-border text-[12px] font-semibold inline-flex items-center gap-1 hover:bg-secondary\"\n              @click=\"addChapterPrompt\"\n            >\n              + Add chapter\n            </button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n            <div\n              v-for=\"ch in chapters\"\n              :key=\"ch.id\"\n              class=\"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card overflow-hidden\"\n            >\n              <div class=\"px-4 py-3 border-b border-border bg-secondary/40\">\n                <div class=\"text-[14px] font-semibold\">{{ ch.idx }}. {{ ch.title }}</div>\n                <div v-if=\"ch.description\" class=\"text-[12px] text-muted-foreground\">\n                  {{ ch.description }}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <ul>\n                <li\n                  v-for=\"l in getLessonsForChapter(ch.id)\"\n                  :key=\"l.id\"\n                  class=\"border-b border-border last:border-0\"\n                >\n                  <RouterLink\n                    :to=\"`/courses/${courseId}/lessons/${l.id}`\"\n                    class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2.5 hover:bg-secondary/40\"\n                  >\n                    <span>{{ isLessonComplete(l.id) ? \"✅\" : \"⭕\" }}</span>\n                    <span class=\"text-[13px] flex-1\">{{ l.title }}</span>\n                    <span v-if=\"l.youtube_video\" class=\"text-[11px] text-muted-foreground\"\n                      >▶ video</span\n                    >\n                  </RouterLink>\n                </li>\n                <li\n                  v-if=\"!getLessonsForChapter(ch.id).length\"\n                  class=\"px-4 py-3 text-[12px] text-muted-foreground\"\n                >\n                  No lessons yet.\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n              <div v-if=\"isAuthor\" class=\"px-4 py-2 border-t border-border bg-background\">\n                <div v-if=\"addLessonForChapter === ch.id\">\n                  <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 py-1\">\n                    <input\n                      v-model=\"lessonTitle\"\n                      placeholder=\"Lesson title\"\n                      autofocus\n                      class=\"h-9 px-3 rounded-md border border-border bg-background text-[13px] outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/30\"\n                    />\n                    <input\n                      v-model=\"lessonYt\"\n                      placeholder=\"YouTube URL (optional)\"\n                      class=\"h-9 px-3 rounded-md border border-border bg-background text-[13px] outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/30\"\n                    />\n                    <textarea\n                      v-model=\"lessonBody\"\n                      placeholder=\"Short description (optional)\"\n                      rows=\"2\"\n                      class=\"px-3 py-2 rounded-md border border-border bg-background text-[13px] outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/30 resize-none\"\n                    />\n                    <div class=\"flex gap-2\">\n                      <button\n                        type=\"button\"\n                        class=\"h-8 px-3 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-[12px] font-semibold\"\n                        @click=\"submitLesson(ch.id)\"\n                      >\n                        Add lesson\n                      </button>\n                      <button\n                        type=\"button\"\n                        class=\"h-8 px-3 rounded-full text-[12px] text-muted-foreground hover:bg-secondary\"\n                        @click=\"addLessonForChapter = null\"\n                      >\n                        Cancel\n                      </button>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <button\n                  v-else\n                  type=\"button\"\n                  class=\"text-[12px] text-primary font-semibold inline-flex items-center gap-1\"\n                  @click=\"addLessonForChapter = ch.id\"\n                >\n                  + Add lesson\n                </button>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n      </template>\n    </div>\n  </AppLayout>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { ref, computed } from \"vue\";\nimport { RouterLink, useRoute, useRouter } from \"vue-router\";\nimport AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\nimport {\n  getCourse,\n  getChaptersForCourse,\n  getLessonsForChapter,\n  getEnrollment,\n  enrollInCourse,\n  courseProgressPercent,\n  isLessonComplete,\n  addChapter,\n  addLesson,\n  getUser,\n  currentUserId,\n} from \"@/data/store\";\n\nconst route = useRoute();\nconst router = useRouter();\nconst courseId = computed(() => route.params.courseId as string);\nconst course = computed(() => getCourse(courseId.value));\nconst chapters = computed(() => getChaptersForCourse(courseId.value));\nconst enr = computed(() => getEnrollment(courseId.value));\nconst pct = computed(() => courseProgressPercent(courseId.value));\nconst isAuthor = computed(() => course.value?.author === currentUserId);\n\nconst addLessonForChapter = ref<string | null>(null);\nconst lessonTitle = ref(\"\");\nconst lessonYt = ref(\"\");\nconst lessonBody = ref(\"\");\n\nfunction addChapterPrompt() {\n  const title = prompt(\"Chapter title?\");\n  if (title) addChapter(courseId.value, title);\n}\n\nfunction submitLesson(chapterId: string) {\n  if (!lessonTitle.value.trim()) return;\n  addLesson({\n    course: courseId.value,\n    chapter: chapterId,\n    title: lessonTitle.value,\n    body: lessonBody.value ? `<p>${lessonBody.value}</p>` : \"\",\n    youtube_video: lessonYt.value,\n  });\n  lessonTitle.value = \"\";\n  lessonYt.value = \"\";\n  lessonBody.value = \"\";\n  addLessonForChapter.value = null;\n}\n\nfunction goToFirst() {\n  const first = chapters.value.flatMap((ch) => getLessonsForChapter(ch.id))[0];\n  if (first) router.push(`/courses/${courseId.value}/lessons/${first.id}`);\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. `CourseNewView.vue` (115 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout>\n    <div class=\"max-w-[640px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6\">\n      <RouterLink\n        to=\"/courses\"\n        class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[12px] text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground mb-3\"\n      >\n        ← All courses\n      </RouterLink>\n      <h1 class=\"text-[24px] font-bold leading-tight\">Create a course</h1>\n      <p class=\"text-[13px] text-muted-foreground mt-1 mb-5\">\n        Mirrors the <code class=\"font-mono\">LMS Course</code> DocType in frappe/lms. After creating\n        you'll be dropped onto the course page where you can add chapters and YouTube-video lessons.\n      </p>\n\n      <form\n        class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-5\"\n        @submit.prevent=\"submit\"\n      >\n        <label class=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n          <span class=\"text-[12px] font-semibold text-secondary-foreground\"\n            >Title <span class=\"text-destructive\">*</span></span\n          >\n          <input\n            v-model=\"title\"\n            required\n            placeholder=\"e.g. Surviving Freshers' Week\"\n            class=\"h-10 px-3 rounded-md border border-border bg-background text-[14px] outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/30\"\n          />\n        </label>\n        <label class=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n          <span class=\"text-[12px] font-semibold text-secondary-foreground\"\n            >Short introduction</span\n          >\n          <input\n            v-model=\"intro\"\n            placeholder=\"One sentence that appears on the card\"\n            class=\"h-10 px-3 rounded-md border border-border bg-background text-[14px] outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/30\"\n          />\n        </label>\n        <label class=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n          <span class=\"text-[12px] font-semibold text-secondary-foreground\">Description</span>\n          <textarea\n            v-model=\"desc\"\n            rows=\"4\"\n            placeholder=\"What learners will get out of this course\"\n            class=\"px-3 py-2 rounded-md border border-border bg-background text-[14px] outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/30 resize-none\"\n          />\n        </label>\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n          <label class=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n            <span class=\"text-[12px] font-semibold text-secondary-foreground\">Category</span>\n            <select\n              v-model=\"category\"\n              class=\"h-10 px-2 rounded-md border border-border bg-background text-[14px]\"\n            >\n              <option>Student Life</option>\n              <option>Writing</option>\n              <option>Money</option>\n              <option>Wellbeing</option>\n              <option>Career</option>\n            </select>\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"flex flex-col gap-1.5\">\n            <span class=\"text-[12px] font-semibold text-secondary-foreground\">Tags</span>\n            <input\n              v-model=\"tags\"\n              placeholder=\"comma, separated\"\n              class=\"h-10 px-3 rounded-md border border-border bg-background text-[14px]\"\n            />\n          </label>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 pt-2\">\n          <button\n            type=\"submit\"\n            class=\"h-10 px-5 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-[14px] font-semibold\"\n          >\n            Create course\n          </button>\n          <RouterLink\n            to=\"/courses\"\n            class=\"h-10 px-4 rounded-full text-[14px] text-muted-foreground hover:bg-secondary inline-flex items-center\"\n            >Cancel</RouterLink\n          >\n        </div>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n  </AppLayout>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { ref } from \"vue\";\nimport { RouterLink, useRouter } from \"vue-router\";\nimport AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\nimport { createCourse } from \"@/data/store\";\n\nconst router = useRouter();\nconst title = ref(\"\");\nconst intro = ref(\"\");\nconst desc = ref(\"\");\nconst category = ref(\"Student Life\");\nconst tags = ref(\"\");\n\nfunction submit() {\n  if (!title.value.trim()) return;\n  const c = createCourse({\n    title: title.value,\n    short_introduction: intro.value,\n    description: desc.value,\n    category: category.value,\n    tags: tags.value,\n  });\n  router.push(`/courses/${c.id}`);\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 8. `LessonView.vue` (126 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout>\n    <div class=\"max-w-[820px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6\">\n      <RouterLink\n        :to=\"`/courses/${courseId}`\"\n        class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[12px] text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground mb-4\"\n      >\n        ← {{ course?.title }}\n      </RouterLink>\n\n      <div v-if=\"!lesson\" class=\"p-12 text-center\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-[18px] font-semibold mb-2\">Lesson not found</h2>\n        <RouterLink to=\"/courses\" class=\"text-primary underline\">Back to courses</RouterLink>\n      </div>\n      <template v-else>\n        <h1 class=\"text-[24px] font-bold leading-tight mb-4\">{{ lesson.title }}</h1>\n\n        <div\n          v-if=\"lesson.youtube_video\"\n          class=\"aspect-video rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-border bg-black mb-4\"\n        >\n          <iframe\n            :title=\"lesson.title\"\n            :src=\"`https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/${lesson.youtube_video}?rel=0`\"\n            allow=\"\n              accelerometer;\n              autoplay;\n              clipboard-write;\n              encrypted-media;\n              gyroscope;\n              picture-in-picture;\n            \"\n            allowfullscreen\n            class=\"w-full h-full\"\n          />\n        </div>\n        <div\n          v-else\n          class=\"aspect-video rounded-xl border border-dashed border-border bg-secondary/40 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-[13px] text-muted-foreground\"\n        >\n          (No video for this lesson — text only)\n        </div>\n\n        <article\n          class=\"text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-secondary-foreground\"\n          v-html=\"lesson.body || '<p></p>'\"\n        />\n\n        <div class=\"mt-6 flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap\">\n          <button\n            v-if=\"!enrolled\"\n            type=\"button\"\n            class=\"h-9 px-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-[13px] font-semibold\"\n            @click=\"enrollInCourse(courseId)\"\n          >\n            Enroll to track progress\n          </button>\n          <button\n            v-if=\"enrolled\"\n            type=\"button\"\n            class=\"h-9 px-4 rounded-full text-[13px] font-semibold inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 border\"\n            :class=\"\n              done\n                ? 'bg-success/10 border-success/30 text-success'\n                : 'bg-primary text-primary-foreground border-primary'\n            \"\n            @click=\"markLessonComplete(lessonId, !done)\"\n          >\n            {{ done ? \"✅ Completed\" : \"⭕ Mark complete\" }}\n          </button>\n        </div>\n\n        <nav class=\"mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-border flex items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n          <button\n            type=\"button\"\n            :disabled=\"!prev\"\n            class=\"h-9 px-3 rounded-full border border-border text-[13px] inline-flex items-center gap-1 disabled:opacity-40\"\n            @click=\"prev && router.push(`/courses/${courseId}/lessons/${prev.id}`)\"\n          >\n            ← {{ prev?.title ?? \"Previous\" }}\n          </button>\n          <button\n            type=\"button\"\n            :disabled=\"!next\"\n            class=\"h-9 px-3 rounded-full border border-border text-[13px] inline-flex items-center gap-1 disabled:opacity-40\"\n            @click=\"next && router.push(`/courses/${courseId}/lessons/${next.id}`)\"\n          >\n            {{ next?.title ?? \"Next\" }} →\n          </button>\n        </nav>\n      </template>\n    </div>\n  </AppLayout>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { computed } from \"vue\";\nimport { RouterLink, useRoute, useRouter } from \"vue-router\";\nimport AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\nimport {\n  getCourse,\n  getLesson,\n  getChaptersForCourse,\n  getLessonsForChapter,\n  isLessonComplete,\n  markLessonComplete,\n  getEnrollment,\n  enrollInCourse,\n} from \"@/data/store\";\n\nconst route = useRoute();\nconst router = useRouter();\nconst courseId = computed(() => route.params.courseId as string);\nconst lessonId = computed(() => route.params.lessonId as string);\nconst course = computed(() => getCourse(courseId.value));\nconst lesson = computed(() => getLesson(lessonId.value));\nconst done = computed(() => isLessonComplete(lessonId.value));\nconst enrolled = computed(() => !!getEnrollment(courseId.value));\n\nconst flat = computed(() =>\n  getChaptersForCourse(courseId.value).flatMap((ch) => getLessonsForChapter(ch.id)),\n);\nconst idx = computed(() => flat.value.findIndex((l) => l.id === lessonId.value));\nconst prev = computed(() => (idx.value > 0 ? flat.value[idx.value - 1] : null));\nconst next = computed(() => (idx.value < flat.value.length - 1 ? flat.value[idx.value + 1] : null));\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 9. `MentorsView.vue` (150 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout>\n    <div class=\"max-w-[920px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6\">\n      <header class=\"mb-5\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-[24px] font-bold leading-tight\">Mentor Match</h1>\n        <p class=\"text-[14px] text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">\n          Mentors here are other students and staff who've been where you are.\n        </p>\n      </header>\n\n      <!-- My matches -->\n      <section class=\"mb-8\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-[14px] font-semibold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">\n          My matches\n        </h2>\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n          <div v-if=\"matches.length === 0\" class=\"text-[13px] text-muted-foreground\">\n            No matches yet — request one below.\n          </div>\n          <div\n            v-for=\"m in matches\"\n            :key=\"m.id\"\n            class=\"rounded-xl bg-card border border-border p-4 flex items-center gap-3\"\n          >\n            <AppAvatar :user-id=\"getOtherUserId(m)\" :size=\"40\" />\n            <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n              <div class=\"text-[14px] font-semibold truncate\">\n                {{ getUser(getOtherUserId(m))?.full_name }}\n                <span class=\"text-muted-foreground font-normal ml-1\"\n                  >({{ m.mentee === currentUserId ? \"your mentor\" : \"your mentee\" }})</span\n                >\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"text-[12px] text-muted-foreground truncate\">{{ m.match_notes }}</div>\n            </div>\n            <span\n              class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full\"\n              :class=\"statusStyles[m.status]\"\n              >{{ m.status }}</span\n            >\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <!-- Find a mentor -->\n      <section>\n        <h2 class=\"text-[14px] font-semibold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">\n          Find a mentor\n        </h2>\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n          <div\n            v-for=\"u in candidates\"\n            :key=\"u.user\"\n            class=\"rounded-xl bg-card border border-border p-5 flex flex-col items-center text-center\"\n          >\n            <AppAvatar :user-id=\"u.user\" :size=\"56\" />\n            <RouterLink\n              :to=\"`/members/${u.user}`\"\n              class=\"mt-3 text-[14px] font-semibold hover:text-primary\"\n              >{{ u.full_name }}</RouterLink\n            >\n            <p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-muted-foreground line-clamp-3 mb-3\">{{ u.bio }}</p>\n            <button\n              type=\"button\"\n              class=\"mt-auto h-8 px-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-[12px] font-semibold\"\n              @click=\"selected = u.user\"\n            >\n              Request match\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <!-- Request modal -->\n      <div\n        v-if=\"selected\"\n        class=\"fixed inset-0 bg-foreground/30 flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-50\"\n        @click=\"selected = null\"\n      >\n        <div class=\"bg-card rounded-2xl p-6 max-w-md w-full shadow-2xl\" @click.stop>\n          <h3 class=\"text-[16px] font-semibold mb-1\">\n            Request {{ getUser(selected)?.full_name }} as a mentor\n          </h3>\n          <p class=\"text-[12px] text-muted-foreground mb-3\">\n            A short note about what you're hoping for helps a lot.\n          </p>\n          <textarea\n            v-model=\"notes\"\n            rows=\"4\"\n            placeholder=\"e.g. I'd love help navigating my first essays and getting comfortable with office hours.\"\n            class=\"w-full bg-secondary/60 rounded-lg p-3 text-[14px] outline-none resize-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/30\"\n          />\n          <div class=\"flex justify-end gap-2 mt-3\">\n            <button\n              type=\"button\"\n              class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold h-8 px-3 rounded-full hover:bg-secondary\"\n              @click=\"selected = null\"\n            >\n              Cancel\n            </button>\n            <button\n              type=\"button\"\n              class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold h-8 px-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground\"\n              @click=\"sendRequest\"\n            >\n              Send request\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </AppLayout>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { ref, computed } from \"vue\";\nimport { RouterLink } from \"vue-router\";\nimport AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\nimport AppAvatar from \"@/components/AppAvatar.vue\";\nimport { currentUserId, getMatchesForUser, getUser, getUsers, requestMentor } from \"@/data/store\";\nimport type { FGMentorMatch } from \"@/mock-data/types\";\n\nconst matches = computed(() => getMatchesForUser(currentUserId));\nconst myMentorIds = computed(\n  () => new Set(matches.value.filter((m) => m.mentee === currentUserId).map((m) => m.mentor)),\n);\nconst candidates = computed(() =>\n  getUsers().filter((u) => u.user !== currentUserId && !myMentorIds.value.has(u.user)),\n);\n\nconst selected = ref<string | null>(null);\nconst notes = ref(\"\");\n\nconst statusStyles: Record<string, string> = {\n  Requested: \"bg-flag/30 text-flag-foreground\",\n  Active: \"bg-primary-soft text-primary-soft-foreground\",\n  Completed: \"bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground\",\n  \"Ended Early\": \"bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground\",\n};\n\nfunction getOtherUserId(m: FGMentorMatch) {\n  return m.mentee === currentUserId ? m.mentor : m.mentee;\n}\n\nfunction sendRequest() {\n  if (!selected.value) return;\n  requestMentor(selected.value, notes.value || \"—\");\n  selected.value = null;\n  notes.value = \"\";\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 10. `MessagesView.vue` (62 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout>\n    <div class=\"flex h-[calc(100vh-3.5rem)]\">\n      <!-- Thread list sidebar -->\n      <aside class=\"w-72 shrink-0 border-r border-border bg-surface overflow-y-auto\">\n        <div class=\"px-4 py-3 border-b border-border\">\n          <h1 class=\"text-[16px] font-bold\">Direct messages</h1>\n          <p class=\"text-[12px] text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">\n            In-memory mock · maps to Raven channels\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <ul class=\"flex flex-col\">\n          <li v-for=\"t in threads\" :key=\"t.id\">\n            <RouterLink\n              :to=\"`/messages/${t.id}`\"\n              class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 border-b border-border/60 transition-colors\"\n              :class=\"route.path === `/messages/${t.id}` ? 'bg-primary-soft' : 'hover:bg-secondary'\"\n            >\n              <AppAvatar :user-id=\"getOtherMember(t)\" :size=\"36\" />\n              <div class=\"min-w-0 flex-1\">\n                <div class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold truncate\">\n                  {{ getUser(getOtherMember(t))?.full_name }}\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-[12px] text-muted-foreground truncate\">\n                  {{ t.last_message_preview || \"No messages yet\" }}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </RouterLink>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </aside>\n\n      <!-- Thread content or empty state -->\n      <section class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n        <RouterView v-if=\"route.params.threadId\" />\n        <div v-else class=\"h-full flex items-center justify-center text-center px-6\">\n          <div class=\"max-w-sm\">\n            <div class=\"text-4xl mb-2\">💬</div>\n            <h2 class=\"text-[16px] font-semibold\">Pick a conversation</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-[13px] text-muted-foreground mt-1\">\n              Start a new one from any member's profile, or open one on the left.\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"text-[11px] text-muted-foreground mt-3\">\n              Signed in as <strong>{{ getUser(currentUserId)?.full_name }}</strong>\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n  </AppLayout>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { computed } from \"vue\";\nimport { RouterLink, RouterView, useRoute } from \"vue-router\";\nimport AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\nimport AppAvatar from \"@/components/AppAvatar.vue\";\nimport { getDMThreadsForUser, getOtherMember, getUser, currentUserId } from \"@/data/store\";\n\nconst route = useRoute();\nconst threads = computed(() => getDMThreadsForUser());\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 11. `ThreadView.vue` (108 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <div class=\"flex flex-col h-full\">\n    <div v-if=\"!thread\" class=\"p-6 text-[14px]\">\n      Thread not found.\n      <RouterLink to=\"/messages\" class=\"text-primary underline\">Back to messages</RouterLink>\n    </div>\n    <template v-else>\n      <header class=\"h-14 px-4 border-b border-border flex items-center gap-3 bg-surface\">\n        <AppAvatar :user-id=\"other.user\" :size=\"32\" />\n        <div class=\"min-w-0\">\n          <div class=\"text-[14px] font-semibold truncate\">{{ other.full_name }}</div>\n          <div class=\"text-[11px] text-muted-foreground truncate\">{{ other.bio }}</div>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n\n      <div\n        ref=\"scrollRef\"\n        class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-4 py-5 flex flex-col gap-3 bg-background\"\n      >\n        <div\n          v-for=\"m in messages\"\n          :key=\"m.id\"\n          class=\"flex gap-2\"\n          :class=\"m.sender === currentUserId ? 'justify-end' : 'justify-start'\"\n        >\n          <AppAvatar v-if=\"m.sender !== currentUserId\" :user-id=\"m.sender\" :size=\"28\" />\n          <div\n            class=\"max-w-[70%] rounded-2xl px-3.5 py-2 text-[14px] leading-snug whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\"\n            :class=\"\n              m.sender === currentUserId\n                ? 'bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-br-sm'\n                : 'bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground rounded-bl-sm'\n            \"\n          >\n            {{ m.content }}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div\n          v-if=\"messages.length === 0\"\n          class=\"text-center text-[13px] text-muted-foreground py-10\"\n        >\n          Say hi 👋\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <form\n        class=\"border-t border-border bg-surface p-3 flex items-end gap-2\"\n        @submit.prevent=\"send\"\n      >\n        <textarea\n          v-model=\"draft\"\n          :placeholder=\"`Message ${other.full_name}`\"\n          rows=\"1\"\n          class=\"flex-1 resize-none rounded-xl border border-border bg-background px-3 py-2 text-[14px] outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/30 max-h-32\"\n          @keydown.enter.exact.prevent=\"send\"\n        />\n        <button\n          type=\"submit\"\n          :disabled=\"!draft.trim()\"\n          class=\"h-9 px-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-[13px] font-semibold disabled:opacity-40\"\n        >\n          Send\n        </button>\n      </form>\n    </template>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { ref, computed, watch, nextTick, onMounted } from \"vue\";\nimport { RouterLink, useRoute } from \"vue-router\";\nimport AppAvatar from \"@/components/AppAvatar.vue\";\nimport {\n  currentUserId,\n  getDMMessages,\n  getDMThread,\n  getOtherMember,\n  getUser,\n  markThreadRead,\n  sendDM,\n} from \"@/data/store\";\n\nconst route = useRoute();\nconst threadId = computed(() => route.params.threadId as string);\nconst thread = computed(() => getDMThread(threadId.value));\nconst other = computed(() => {\n  const t = thread.value;\n  if (!t) return null;\n  return getUser(getOtherMember(t))!;\n});\nconst messages = computed(() => getDMMessages(threadId.value));\nconst draft = ref(\"\");\nconst scrollRef = ref<HTMLDivElement | null>(null);\n\nonMounted(() => markThreadRead(threadId.value));\nwatch(threadId, () => markThreadRead(threadId.value));\n\nwatch(\n  () => messages.value.length,\n  () => nextTick(() => scrollRef.value?.scrollTo({ top: scrollRef.value.scrollHeight })),\n);\n\nfunction send() {\n  if (!draft.value.trim()) return;\n  sendDM(threadId.value, draft.value);\n  draft.value = \"\";\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 12. `NotificationsView.vue` (79 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout>\n    <div class=\"max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6\">\n      <header class=\"mb-5 flex items-center justify-between\">\n        <div>\n          <h1 class=\"text-[24px] font-bold leading-tight\">Notifications</h1>\n          <p class=\"text-[13px] text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">\n            Maps 1:1 to Frappe <code class=\"font-mono\">Notification Log</code>.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <button\n          type=\"button\"\n          class=\"h-8 px-3 rounded-full bg-secondary text-[12px] font-semibold hover:bg-secondary/70\"\n          @click=\"markAllNotificationsRead()\"\n        >\n          Mark all read\n        </button>\n      </header>\n\n      <ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n        <li v-for=\"n in items\" :key=\"n.id\">\n          <component\n            :is=\"linkFor(n) ? RouterLink : 'div'\"\n            :to=\"linkFor(n) || undefined\"\n            @click=\"linkFor(n) && markNotificationRead(n.id)\"\n          >\n            <div\n              class=\"flex items-start gap-3 rounded-xl border p-4 transition-colors\"\n              :class=\"n.read ? 'border-border bg-card' : 'border-primary/30 bg-primary-soft/50'\"\n            >\n              <div class=\"text-xl\">{{ iconFor(n.type) }}</div>\n              <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n                <div class=\"text-[14px] font-semibold\">{{ n.subject }}</div>\n                <div class=\"text-[12px] text-muted-foreground mt-0.5\">\n                  {{ n.type }} · {{ new Date(n.created_at).toLocaleString() }}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <span v-if=\"!n.read\" class=\"size-2 rounded-full bg-primary mt-1.5\" />\n            </div>\n          </component>\n        </li>\n        <li v-if=\"items.length === 0\" class=\"text-center text-[13px] text-muted-foreground py-10\">\n          You're all caught up.\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </AppLayout>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { onMounted, computed } from \"vue\";\nimport { RouterLink } from \"vue-router\";\nimport AppLayout from \"@/components/AppLayout.vue\";\nimport { getNotifications, markAllNotificationsRead, markNotificationRead } from \"@/data/store\";\nimport type { FGNotification } from \"@/mock-data/types\";\n\nconst items = computed(() => getNotifications());\n\nonMounted(() => setTimeout(() => markAllNotificationsRead(), 800));\n\nfunction iconFor(t: FGNotification[\"type\"]) {\n  return { DM: \"💬\", Reply: \"↩️\", Mention: \"@\", Event: \"📅\", Mentor: \"🤝\" }[t] ?? \"🔔\";\n}\n\nfunction linkFor(n: FGNotification): string | null {\n  switch (n.document_type) {\n    case \"GP Discussion\":\n      return `/posts/${n.document_name}`;\n    case \"FG DM Thread\":\n      return `/messages/${n.document_name}`;\n    case \"FG Event\":\n      return \"/events\";\n    case \"FG Mentor Match\":\n      return \"/mentors\";\n    default:\n      return null;\n  }\n}\n</script>\n```\n\n---\n\n### 13. `PostDetailView.vue` (210 lines)\n\n```vue\n<template>\n  <AppLayout :space-context-id=\"post?.project\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-6\">\n      <div v-if=\"!post\" class=\"p-12 text-center\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-[18px] font-semibold mb-2\">Post not found</h2>\n        <RouterLink to=\"/\" class=\"text-primary underline\">Back home</RouterLink>\n      </div>\n      <template v-else>\n        <RouterLink\n          v-if=\"project\"\n          :to=\"`/spaces/${project.id}`\"\n          class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[12px] text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground mb-4\"\n        >\n          ← {{ project.icon }} {{ project.title }}\n        </RouterLink>\n\n        <article class=\"rounded-xl bg-card border border-border p-6\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\">\n            <AppAvatar :user-id=\"post.author_id\" :size=\"40\" />\n            <div>\n              <RouterLink\n                :to=\"`/members/${post.author_id}`\"\n                class=\"block text-[14px] font-semibold leading-tight hover:text-primary\"\n              >\n                {{ getUser(post.author_id)?.full_name }}\n              </RouterLink>\n              <div class=\"text-[12px] text-muted-foreground\">{{ formatDate(post.created_at) }}</div>\n            </div>\n            <div v-if=\"sent\" class=\"ml-auto\">\n              <SentimentBadge :sentiment=\"sent\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <h1 class=\"text-[24px] font-bold leading-tight mb-3\">{{ post.title }}</h1>\n          <div\n            class=\"text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-secondary-foreground [&_p]:mb-3 [&_em]:italic\"\n            v-html=\"post.content\"\n          />\n\n          <!-- Reactions -->\n          <div class=\"mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5\">\n            <button\n              v-for=\"emoji in QUICK_EMOJIS\"\n              :key=\"emoji\"\n              class=\"h-7 px-2.5 rounded-full border text-[13px] inline-flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors\"\n              :class=\"\n                myReactions.has(emoji)\n                  ? 'bg-primary-soft border-primary/40 text-primary-soft-foreground'\n                  : 'bg-card border-border hover:bg-secondary'\n              \"\n              @click=\"toggleReaction('GP Discussion', postId, emoji)\"\n            >\n              <span>{{ emoji }}</span>\n              <span v-if=\"(reactionCounts[emoji] ?? 0) > 0\" class=\"text-[12px] font-semibold\">{{\n                reactionCounts[emoji]\n              }}</span>\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <!-- Comments -->\n        <section class=\"mt-6\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-[16px] font-semibold mb-3\">\n            {{ comments.length }} {{ comments.length === 1 ? \"comment\" : \"comments\" }}\n          </h2>\n\n          <!-- Reply composer -->\n          <form\n            class=\"rounded-xl bg-card border border-border p-3 mb-4 focus-within:border-border-strong\"\n            @submit.prevent=\"submitReply\"\n          >\n            <div class=\"flex gap-3\">\n              <AppAvatar :user-id=\"currentUserId\" :size=\"32\" />\n              <div class=\"flex-1\">\n                <textarea\n                  v-model=\"reply\"\n                  placeholder=\"Add a comment…\"\n                  rows=\"2\"\n                  class=\"w-full bg-transparent text-[14px] outline-none resize-none placeholder:text-muted-foreground\"\n                />\n                <div class=\"flex justify-end\">\n                  <button\n                    type=\"submit\"\n                    :disabled=\"!reply.trim()\"\n                    class=\"h-8 px-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-[13px] font-semibold disabled:opacity-40\"\n                  >\n                    Post\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </form>\n\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\">\n            <div\n              v-for=\"c in comments\"\n              :key=\"c.id\"\n              class=\"rounded-xl bg-card border border-border p-4\"\n            >\n              <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-2\">\n                <AppAvatar :user-id=\"c.author_id\" :size=\"28\" />\n                <div class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold\">{{ getUser(c.author_id)?.full_name }}</div>\n                <span class=\"text-[11px] text-muted-foreground\">{{\n                  formatDateTime(c.created_at)\n                }}</span>\n              </div>\n              <div\n                class=\"text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-secondary-foreground [&_p]:mb-2\"\n                v-html=\"c.content\"\n              />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- Similar posts -->\n        <aside v-if=\"similar.length\" class=\"mt-8 rounded-xl bg-card border border-border p-5\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n            <span class=\"text-primary\">✨</span>\n            <h3 class=\"text-[14px] font-semibold\">Similar conversations</h3>\n            <span\n              class=\"ml-auto text-[11px] text-muted-foreground\"\n              title=\"Mocked — production uses EmbeddingGemma + vector search.\"\n              >mocked</span\n            >\n          </div>\n          <ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n            <li v-for=\"s in similar\" :key=\"s.id\">\n              <RouterLink\n                :to=\"`/posts/${s.id}`\"\n\n...21159 bytes truncated...\n\nThe tool call succeeded but the output was truncated. Full output saved to: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.local\\share\\opencode\\tool-output\\tool_ee45dc1b1001MAY2udWtZ77p4C\nUse the Task tool to have explore agent process this file with Grep and Read (with offset/limit). Do NOT read the f