      "text": "Now I have a complete understanding of the codebase. Let me now read the remaining view files that were truncated (SpaceView, SettingsView, DocsView, PostDetailView) and then start making all the fixes needed.\n\nActually, I already have the PostDetailView content from the task output. Let me read the remaining files I need.\n\nLet me now focus on the major fixes needed:\n\n1. **MentorsView** - Add \"Message\" button to match cards (Gherkin scenario 1)\n2. **MembersView** - Add filter UI and action buttons (Gherkin scenario 4)\n\n\n3. **HomeView** - Ensure cross-space feed works properly (Gherkin scenario 12)\n4. **SpaceView** - Make sure it renders correctly\n5. **PostDetailView** - Verify reactions and comments work\n6. **SettingsView** - Verify all tabs work\n\nI need to tackle these systematically, starting with the MentorsView to add the \"Message\" button on match cards as specified in the Gherkin scenarios.",
