      "type": "answer",
      "text": "All user journeys are now working. Here's what was fixed and added:\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\n### Gherkin Scenario Fixes\n\n| Scenario | What was added |\n|---|---|\n| **1. DMs (Raven)** | \"Message\" button on active mentor match cards in MentorsView |\n| **4. Member Directory** | Search/filter bar + \"Message\" and \"View profile\" buttons on member cards |\n| **7. Polls** | New `PollCard` component with voting, percentage display, vote counts; integrated into PostCard; poll types + seed data |\n| **8. Gamification** | Badge system (6 badge types), badge awards, energy points; displayed on member profile Achievements section |\n| **12. Cross-space feed** | Already working — home feed shows all posts across spaces sorted by recency |\n\n### New Features Added\n\n| Feature | Files |\n|---|---|\n| **PollCard component** | `src/components/PollCard.vue` — vote, show percentages, animated bars |\n| **Poll types & seed** | `types.ts`, `seed.ts` — `FGPoll`, `FGPollVote`, 2 seed polls with votes |\n| **Badge system** | `types.ts`, `seed.ts` — `FGBadge`, `FGBadgeAward`, 6 badge types, 10 seed awards |\n| **Energy Points** | Seed data for all 6 users, selectors and mutators |\n| **Create Event** | EventsView new event modal, `createEvent()` store function |\n| **Search Members** | MembersView search bar filtering by name/bio |\n| **New Event Modal** | Full form with title, description, date, type |\n| **Docs index** | DocsView now lists all 12 doc files |\n\n### Store Mutations (all working)\n\n| Flow | Function | Status |\n|---|---|---|\n| Create post | `createDiscussion()` | ✅ |\n| Post comment | `createComment()` | ✅ |\n| Toggle reaction | `toggleReaction()` | ✅ |\n| RSVP to event | `setRSVP()` | ✅ |\n| Create event | `createEvent()` | ✅ NEW |\n| Request mentor | `requestMentor()` | ✅ |\n| Message from match | `openOrCreateDMWith()` | ✅ NEW |\n| Enroll in course | `enrollInCourse()` | ✅ |\n| Mark lesson complete | `markLessonComplete()` | ✅ |\n| Vote on poll | `votePoll()` | ✅ NEW |\n| Send DM | `sendDM()` | ✅ |\n| Mark thread read | `markThreadRead()` | ✅ |\n| Update settings | `updateUserSettings()` | ✅ |\n| Update profile | `updateProfile()` | ✅ |\n| Toggle SSO | `updateSSOProvider()` | ✅ |\n| Award badge | `awardBadgeIfNew()` | ✅ NEW |\n| Add energy points | `addEnergyPoints()` | ✅ NEW |\n\n**Build: ✅ PASS (801ms)**",
