      "tool": "task",
      "code": "{\"description\": \"Check Frappe ecosystem repos\", \"prompt\": \"I need you to research the following Frappe ecosystem repos and return key information about their DocType structures, API endpoints, and how they work. This is for verifying a prototype that maps to these repos.\\n\\nFetch and analyze these repos:\\n\\n1. https://github.com/frappe/gameplan - Focus on GP Team, GP Project, GP Discussion, GP Comment, GP Reaction, GP User Profile DocTypes. What fields do they have?\\n\\n2. https://github.com/frappe/lms - Focus on LMS Course, LMS Chapter, LMS Lesson, LMS Enrollment, LMS Course Progress, LMS Certificate DocTypes. What fields do they have?\\n\\n3. https://github.com/The-Commit-Company/Raven - Focus on Raven Channel, Raven Message DocTypes for DMs.\\n\\n4. https://github.com/frappe/helpdesk - Focus on HD Ticket DocType for support/safeguarding.\\n\\n5. https://github.com/frappe/eps - Focus on Energy Points System DocTypes.\\n\\n6. https://github.com/frappe/payments - Focus on payment/subscription DocTypes for billing/paywall.\\n\\nFor each repo, return:\\n- The main DocType JSON field definitions (field names, fieldtypes)\\n- Any custom fields or hooks\\n- Key API endpoints (@frappe.whitelist)\\n\\nReturn a comprehensive summary I can use to verify the prototype's type definitions match.\", \"subagent_type\": \"general\"}",
      "output": "<task id=\"ses_11b973f84ffeEcJdDKxroIq5SA\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\nNow I have comprehensive data from all repositories. Here's the complete summary:\n\n---\n\n# Frappe Ecosystem DocType Reference Summary\n\n## 1. Gameplan (Discussions Platform)\n\n### GP Team\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `title` | Data | Yes | |\n| `icon` | Data | No | |\n| `is_private` | Check | No | Default: 0 |\n| `members` | Table | No | Options: \"GP Member\" |\n| `cover_image` | Attach Image | No | |\n| `cover_image_position` | Float | No | |\n| `readme` | Text Editor | No | |\n| `archived_by` | Link→User | No | |\n| `archived_at` | Datetime | No | |\n\n### GP Project\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `title` | Data | Yes | |\n| `icon` | Data | No | |\n| `team` | Link→GP Team | No | in_standard_filter |\n| `is_private` | Check | No | Default: 0 |\n| `description` | Text Editor | No | |\n| `readme` | Text Editor | No | |\n| `members` | Table | No | Options: \"GP Member\" |\n| `tasks_count` | Int | No | |\n| `discussions_count` | Int | No | |\n| `archived_at` | Datetime | No | |\n| `archived_by` | Link→User | No | |\n| `is_followed` | Check (virtual) | No | Default: 0 |\n\n### GP Discussion\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `project` | Link→GP Project | Yes | search_index |\n| `team` | Link→GP Team | No | fetch_from: project.team |\n| `status` | Data | No | |\n| `title` | Data | Yes | |\n| `slug` | Data | No | |\n| `content` | Text Editor | No | read_only, ignore_xss_filter |\n| `reactions` | Table | No | Options: \"GP Reaction\" |\n| `tags` | Table | No | Options: \"GP Tag Link\" |\n| `last_post_at` | Datetime | No | |\n| `last_post_type` | Select | No | Options: GP Comment, GP Poll |\n| `last_post` | Dynamic Link | No | Options: last_post_type |\n| `last_post_by` | Link→User | No | |\n| `closed_at` | Datetime | No | |\n| `closed_by` | Link→User | No | |\n| `pinned_at` | Datetime | No | |\n| `pin_scope` | Select | No | Options: Global, Space |\n| `pinned_by` | Link→User | No | |\n| `comments_count` | Int | No | read_only |\n| `participants_count` | Int | No | read_only |\n\n### GP Comment\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `content` | Text Editor | Yes | ignore_xss_filter |\n| `reference_doctype` | Link→DocType | No | |\n| `reference_name` | Dynamic Link | No | Options: reference_doctype |\n| `edited_at` | Datetime | No | |\n| `deleted_at` | Datetime | No | |\n| `reactions` | Table | No | Options: \"GP Reaction\" |\n| `tags` | Table | No | Options: \"GP Tag Link\" |\n\n### GP Reaction (Child Table)\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `emoji` | Data | Yes | |\n| `user` | Data | No | read_only |\n\n### GP User Profile\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `user` | Link→User | Yes | unique |\n| `enabled` | Check | No | fetch_from: user.enabled |\n| `full_name` | Data | No | fetch_from: user.full_name, read_only |\n| `bio` | Data | No | length: 280 |\n| `readme` | Text Editor | No | |\n| `cover_image` | Attach Image | No | |\n| `cover_image_position` | Float | No | |\n| `image` | Attach Image | No | |\n| `is_image_background_removed` | Check | No | |\n| `original_image` | Attach Image | No | |\n| `image_background_color` | Color | No | |\n\n---\n\n## 2. LMS (Learning Management System)\n\n### LMS Course\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `title` | Data | Yes | |\n| `video_link` | Data | No | Video Embed Link |\n| `tags` | Data | No | |\n| `instructors` | Table MultiSelect | Yes | Options: \"Course Instructor\" |\n| `category` | Link→LMS Category | No | |\n| `status` | Select | No | Options: In Progress, Under Review, Approved (hidden) |\n| `image` | Attach Image | No | |\n| `card_gradient` | Select | No | Red/Blue/Green/Amber/Cyan/Orange/Pink/Purple/Teal/Violet/Yellow/Gray |\n| `published` | Check | No | is_published_field |\n| `published_on` | Date | No | |\n| `upcoming` | Check | No | |\n| `featured` | Check | No | |\n| `disable_self_learning` | Check | No | |\n| `short_introduction` | Small Text | Yes | |\n| `description` | Text Editor | Yes | |\n| `chapters` | Table | No | Options: \"Chapter Reference\" |\n| `related_courses` | Table | No | Options: \"Related Courses\" |\n| `paid_course` | Check | No | |\n| `paid_certificate` | Check | No | |\n| `enable_certification` | Check | No | |\n| `course_price` | Currency | No | mandatory_depends_on |\n| `currency` | Link→Currency | No | mandatory_depends_on |\n| `amount_usd` | Currency | No | |\n| `evaluator` | Link→Course Evaluator | No | depends_on: paid_certificate |\n| `timezone` | Data | No | depends_on: paid_certificate |\n| `enrollments` | Int | No | read_only |\n| `lessons` | Int | No | read_only |\n| `rating` | Data | No | read_only |\n| `notification_sent` | Check | No | read_only |\n\n### LMS Enrollment\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `course` | Link→LMS Course | Yes | fetch_from: batch.course, search_index |\n| `progress` | Float | No | read_only |\n| `payment` | Link→LMS Payment | No | |\n| `current_lesson` | Link→Course Lesson | No | |\n| `enrollment_from_batch` | Link→LMS Batch | No | |\n| `member` | Link→User | Yes | search_index |\n| `member_name` | Data | No | fetch_from: member.full_name, read_only |\n| `member_username` | Data | No | fetch_from: member.username, read_only |\n| `member_image` | Attach Image | No | fetch_from: member.user_image |\n| `purchased_certificate` | Check | No | |\n| `certificate` | Link→LMS Certificate | No | |\n| `member_type` | Select | No | Options: Student, Mentor, Staff |\n| `role` | Select | No | Options: Member, Admin |\n\n### LMS Course Progress\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `member` | Link→User | No | search_index |\n| `member_name` | Data | No | fetch_from: member.full_name, read_only |\n| `status` | Select | No | Options: Complete, Partially Complete, Incomplete |\n| `lesson` | Link→Course Lesson | No | search_index |\n| `chapter` | Link→Course Chapter | No | read_only, search_index |\n| `course` | Link→LMS Course | No | read_only, search_index |\n| `is_scorm_chapter` | Check | No | read_only |\n| `scorm_content` | Long Text | No | read_only |\n\n### LMS Certificate\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `member` | Link→User | Yes | |\n| `member_name` | Data | No | fetch_from: member.full_name, read_only |\n| `evaluator` | Link→Course Evaluator | No | |\n| `evaluator_name` | Data | No | fetch_from: evaluator.full_name, read_only |\n| `issue_date` | Date | Yes | Default: Today |\n| `expiry_date` | Date | No | |\n| `template` | Link→Print Format | Yes | |\n| `published` | Check | No | |\n| `course` | Link→LMS Course | No | |\n| `course_title` | Data | No | fetch_from: course.title, read_only |\n| `batch_name` | Link→LMS Batch | No | |\n| `batch_title` | Data | No | fetch_from: batch_name.title, read_only |\n\n### LMS Batch\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `title` | Data | Yes | |\n| `published` | Check | No | |\n| `start_date` | Date | Yes | |\n| `end_date` | Date | Yes | |\n| `allow_self_enrollment` | Check | No | |\n| `start_time` | Time | Yes | |\n| `end_time` | Time | Yes | |\n| `timezone` | Data | Yes | |\n| `seat_count` | Int | No | |\n| `category` | Link→LMS Category | No | |\n| `evaluation` | Check | No | |\n| `evaluation_end_date` | Date | No | depends_on: evaluation |\n| `certification` | Check | No | |\n| `description` | Small Text | Yes | |\n| `instructors` | Table MultiSelect | Yes | Options: \"Course Instructor\" |\n| `batch_details` | Text Editor | Yes | |\n| `medium` | Select | No | Options: Online, Offline |\n| `courses` | Table | No | Options: \"Batch Course\" |\n| `paid_batch` | Check | No | |\n| `amount` | Currency | No | mandatory_depends_on: paid_batch |\n| `currency` | Link→Currency | No | mandatory_depends_on: paid_batch |\n| `amount_usd` | Currency | No | |\n| `video_link` | Attach | No | |\n| `meta_image` | Attach Image | No | |\n| `timetable` | Table | No | Options: \"LMS Batch Timetable\" |\n| `timetable_template` | Link→LMS Timetable Template | No | |\n| `show_live_class` | Check | No | |\n| `allow_future` | Check | No | Default: 1 |\n| `conferencing_provider` | Select | No | Options: Zoom, Google Meet |\n| `zoom_account` | Link→LMS Zoom Settings | No | |\n| `google_meet_account` | Link→LMS Google Meet Settings | No | |\n| `confirmation_email_template` | Link→Email Template | No | |\n| `custom_component` | Code | No | HTML |\n| `custom_script` | Code | No | Javascript |\n\n### LMS Batch Enrollment\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `member` | Link→User | Yes | |\n| `member_name` | Data | No | fetch_from: member.full_name |\n| `member_username` | Data | No | fetch_from: member.username |\n| `member_image` | Attach Image | No | fetch_from: member.user_image |\n| `batch` | Link→LMS Batch | Yes | |\n| `payment` | Link→LMS Payment | No | |\n| `source` | Link→LMS Source | No | |\n| `confirmation_email_sent` | Check | No | |\n\n---\n\n## 3. Raven (Messaging Platform)\n\n### Raven Channel\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `channel_name` | Data | Yes | read_only_depends_on for DMs |\n| `channel_description` | Small Text | No | |\n| `type` | Select | Yes | Options: Private, Public, Open |\n| `is_synced` | Check | No | read_only |\n| `linked_doctype` | Link→DocType | No | read_only |\n| `linked_document` | Dynamic Link | No | read_only |\n| `workspace` | Link→Raven Workspace | No | search_index |\n| `is_direct_message` | Check | No | set_only_once |\n| `is_thread` | Check | No | read_only |\n| `is_dm_thread` | Check | No | read_only |\n| `is_self_message` | Check | No | set_only_once |\n| `is_archived` | Check | No | |\n| `last_message_timestamp` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `dm_user_1` | Link→Raven User | No | read_only |\n| `dm_user_2` | Link→Raven User | No | read_only |\n| `last_message_details` | JSON | No | read_only |\n| `pinned_messages` | Table | No | Options: \"Raven Pinned Messages\" |\n| `pinned_messages_string` | Small Text | No | |\n| `is_ai_thread` | Check | No | read_only |\n| `openai_thread_id` | Data | No | read_only |\n| `thread_bot` | Link→Raven Bot | No | read_only |\n\n### Raven Message\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `channel_id` | Link→Raven Channel | Yes | search_index |\n| `text` | Long Text | No | |\n| `json` | JSON | No | |\n| `message_reactions` | JSON | No | |\n| `is_reply` | Check | No | |\n| `linked_message` | Link→Raven Message | No | |\n| `replied_message_details` | JSON | No | |\n| `links` | Small Text | No | |\n| `is_thread` | Check | No | |\n| `message_type` | Select | No | Options: Text, Image, File, Poll, System |\n| `content` | Long Text | No | read_only |\n| `file` | Attach | No | |\n| `image_width` | Data | No | |\n| `image_height` | Data | No | |\n| `blurhash` | Small Text | No | |\n| `file_thumbnail` | Attach | No | |\n| `thumbnail_width` | Data | No | |\n| `thumbnail_height` | Data | No | |\n| `link_doctype` | Link→DocType | No | |\n| `link_document` | Dynamic Link | No | search_index |\n| `is_edited` | Check | No | |\n| `is_forwarded` | Check | No | |\n| `mentions` | Table | No | Options: \"Raven Mention\" |\n| `poll_id` | Link→Raven Poll | No | unique |\n| `is_bot_message` | Check | No | |\n| `bot` | Link→Raven User | No | mandatory_depends_on |\n| `hide_link_preview` | Check | No | |\n| `notification` | Data | No | read_only |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Helpdesk (Support/Ticketing)\n\n### HD Ticket\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `subject` | Data | Yes | in_global_search, in_standard_filter |\n| `raised_by` | Data (Email) | No | in_global_search |\n| `status` | Link→HD Ticket Status | No | search_index |\n| `priority` | Link→HD Ticket Priority | No | |\n| `status_category` | Data | No | fetch_from: status.category, read_only |\n| `ticket_type` | Link→HD Ticket Type | No | |\n| `agent_group` | Link→HD Team | No | |\n| `summary` | Text Editor | No | |\n| `description` | Text Editor | No | in_global_search |\n| `template` | Link→HD Ticket Template | No | |\n| `key` | Data | No | read_only, set_only_once |\n| `sla` | Link→HD Service Level Agreement | No | |\n| `response_by` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `raised_outside_working_hours` | Check | No | read_only |\n| `agreement_status` | Select | No | Options: First Response Due, Resolution Due, Failed, Fulfilled, Paused |\n| `resolution_by` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `service_level_agreement_creation` | Datetime | No | hidden, read_only |\n| `on_hold_since` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `total_hold_time` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `first_response_time` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `first_responded_on` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `first_response_failed_by` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `avg_response_time` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `last_agent_response` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `last_customer_response` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `resolution_details` | Text Editor | No | no_copy |\n| `opening_date` | Date | No | read_only |\n| `opening_time` | Time | No | read_only |\n| `resolution_date` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `resolution_time` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `user_resolution_time` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `resolution_failed_by` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `contact` | Link→Contact | No | timeline_field |\n| `customer` | Link→HD Customer | No | |\n| `email_account` | Link→Email Account | No | |\n| `via_customer_portal` | Check | No | |\n| `attachment` | Attach | No | hidden |\n| `content_type` | Data | No | hidden |\n| `is_merged` | Check | No | read_only |\n| `merged_with` | Link→HD Ticket | No | read_only |\n| `ticket_split_from` | Link→HD Ticket | No | read_only |\n| `feedback_rating` | Rating | No | read_only |\n| `feedback` | Link→HD Ticket Feedback Option | No | read_only |\n| `feedback_extra` | Long Text | No | read_only |\n\n---\n\n## 5. EPS (Energy Points System)\n\n### Energy Point Log\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `user` | Link→User | Yes | read_only, search_index |\n| `type` | Select | No | Options: Auto, Appreciation, Criticism, Review, Revert |\n| `points` | Int | No | read_only |\n| `rule` | Link→Energy Point Rule | No | read_only |\n| `reference_doctype` | Link→DocType | No | read_only |\n| `reference_name` | Data | No | read_only |\n| `reverted` | Check | No | hidden |\n| `revert_of` | Link→Energy Point Log | No | read_only |\n| `reason` | Text | No | read_only |\n| `seen` | Check | No | hidden |\n\n### Energy Point Rule\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `enabled` | Check | Yes | Default: 1 |\n| `rule_name` | Data | Yes | unique |\n| `reference_doctype` | Link→DocType | Yes | |\n| `for_doc_event` | Select | No | Options: New, Submit, Cancel, Value Change, Custom |\n| `field_to_check` | Select | No | depends_on: Value Change |\n| `points` | Int | Yes | |\n| `for_assigned_users` | Check | No | |\n| `user_field` | Select | No | |\n| `multiplier_field` | Select | No | |\n| `max_points` | Int | No | |\n| `apply_only_once` | Check | No | |\n| `condition` | Code | No | |\n\n### Energy Point Settings (Singleton)\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `enabled` | Check | No | |\n| `review_levels` | Table | No | Options: \"Review Level\" |\n| `point_allocation_periodicity` | Select | No | Options: Daily, Weekly, Monthly |\n| `last_point_allocation_date` | Date | No | read_only |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Payments (Payment/Subscription)\n\n### Payment Gateway\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `gateway` | Data | Yes | unique, autoname |\n| `gateway_settings` | Link→DocType | No | |\n| `gateway_controller` | Dynamic Link | No | Options: gateway_settings |\n\n---\n\n## Key Relationships Map\n\n```\nGameplan:\n  GP Team ──< GP Project (team)\n  GP Project ──< GP Discussion (project)\n  GP Discussion ──< GP Comment (reference_doctype)\n  GP Discussion ──< GP Reaction (reactions table)\n  GP Comment ──< GP Reaction (reactions table)\n  User ──── GP User Profile (user)\n\nLMS:\n  LMS Course ──< Course Chapter ──< Course Lesson\n  LMS Course ──< LMS Enrollment\n  LMS Batch ──< LMS Batch Enrollment\n  LMS Course ──< LMS Course Progress\n  LMS Course ──< LMS Certificate\n\nRaven:\n  Raven Channel ──< Raven Channel Member\n  Raven Channel ──< Raven Message (channel_id)\n  Raven Message ──< Raven Mention (mentions table)\n\nHelpdesk:\n  HD Ticket ──< HD Ticket Comment\n  HD Team ──< HD Agent\n  HD Service Level Agreement ──< HD Ticket\n\nEPS:\n  Energy Point Rule ──> Energy Point Log\n  User ──── Energy Point Log (user)\n```\n\n## Frappe Field Types Reference\n- **Data**: Text field\n- **Text Editor**: Rich text (HTML)\n- **Small Text**: Multi-line text\n- **Long Text**: Large text block\n- **Link**: Foreign key (options = target DocType)\n- **Dynamic Link**: FK where target is specified by another field\n- **Table**: Child table (options = child DocType)\n- **Table MultiSelect**: Multi-select from child table\n- **Check**: Boolean (0/1)\n- **Select**: Dropdown (options = newline-separated)\n- **Attach/Attach Image**: File upload\n- **Date/Datetime/Time**: Date/time fields\n- **Int/Float/Currency**: Numeric\n- **JSON**: JSON data storage\n- **Code**: Code editor (options = language)\n- **Color**: Color picker\n- **Rating**: Star rating\n</task_result>\n</task>",
      "status": "success",
      "timestamp": 1781948530814
    },
    {
