    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "Now I have comprehensive data from all the Frappe ecosystem repos. Let me compare our prototype's type definitions with the actual Frappe DocType fields and identify gaps.\n\nLet me analyze the gaps:\n\n1. **GP Discussion** - Our prototype is missing:\n   - `last_post_type` (Select: GP Comment, GP Poll)\n   - `last_post` (Dynamic Link)\n   - `pin_scope` (Select: Global, Space)\n   - `reactions` as a child table (we store reactions separately)\n\n2. **GP Comment** - Our prototype is missing:\n   - `edited_at` field\n   - `reactions` as a child table\n\n3. **GP Reaction** - Our prototype has:\n   - `reference_doctype` and `reference_name` (Frappe uses embedded child table)\n   - `user` as Data (Frappe uses same)\n\n4. **LMS Course** - Our prototype is missing several fields:\n   - `instructors` (Table MultiSelect)\n   - `card_gradient` (Select)\n   - `published_on` (Date)\n   - `upcoming` (Check)\n   - `disable_self_learning` (Check)\n   - `chapters` (Table)\n   - `related_courses` (Table)\n   - `paid_certificate` (Check)\n   - `course_price` (Currency)\n   - `currency` (Link)\n   - `amount_usd` (Currency)\n   - `evaluator` (Link)\n   - `timezone` (Data)\n   - `rating` (Data)\n   - `notification_sent` (Check)\n\n5. **LMS Enrollment** - Our prototype is missing:\n   - `payment` (Link)\n   - `current_lesson` (Link)\n   - `enrollment_from_batch` (Link)\n   - `member_name`, `member_username`, `member_image`\n   - `purchased_certificate` (Check)\n   - `certificate` (Link)\n   - `role` (Select)\n\n6. **LMS Course Progress** - Our prototype has:\n   - `status` as \"Complete\" | \"Incomplete\" (Frappe has \"Complete\", \"Partially Complete\", \"Incomplete\")\n   - `chapter` field (Frappe has it)\n\n7. **LMS Chapter** - We don't have a separate Chapter type, we use `LMSChapter` which maps to `Chapter Reference` in Frappe.\n\n8. **Raven Channel** - Our prototype has:\n   - `member_a` and `member_b` (Frappe uses `dm_user_1` and `dm_user_2`)\n   - Missing `is_direct_message`, `is_thread`, `is_dm_thread`, `is_self_message`\n\n9. **Raven Message** - Our prototype has:\n   - `content` field (Frappe uses `text` for Long Text)\n   - Missing `message_type`, `file`, `image_width`, `image_height`, `mentions`\n\n10. **HD Ticket** - We don't have support ticket types yet, need to add them.\n\n11. **EPS** - We have a simplified version with badges and energy points, but Frappe uses `Energy Point Log` and `Energy Point Rule`.\n\n12. **Payments** - We don't have billing/paywall integration yet, need to add frappe/payments.\n\nThe main gaps are billing integration with frappe/payments, support ticket types from frappe/helpdesk, and some missing fields in LMS and Raven types. I need to update our prototype types to align more closely with the actual Frappe DocType structures, especially adding billing and paywall support since that's a key feature the user mentioned.",
