      "type": "answer",
      "text": "## Goal\nFix the Community Launchpad prototype (Vue 3 + Vite 8 + Tailwind v4) — make all user journeys work per Gherkin scenarios, verify all Frappe ecosystem DocType mappings are correct, and ensure the app is fully functional at `http://localhost:8080`.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Production target stack: Frappe Framework + Gameplan + LMS + Raven + Helpdesk + Wiki + EPS + payments\n- App should look and behave like Circle.so (designed in Lovable, refactored to Vue 3)\n- In-memory mock store today, TypeScript types 1:1 mirror real Frappe DocType field names\n- Billing by Frappe (frappe/payments) should be integrated — \"it should just work\"\n- Backup folder required before making changes\n- Each version marked as working on it\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Created backup at `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\community-launchpad-proto-backup-pre-fix`\n- Fixed missing `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin (was causing completely unstyled page)\n- Removed 46 leftover React `.tsx` files from `src/components/ui/` and `src/hooks/`\n- Cleaned `package.json`: removed `lucide-react`, renamed from `tanstack_start_ts` to `community-launchpad-proto`\n- Updated README.md: React 19/TanStack → Vue 3/Vue Router 4 throughout\n- ESLint config verified working (no React plugins, Vue plugins only)\n- Added \"Message\" button to mentor match cards (Gherkin scenario 1: DMs)\n- Added search/filter + action buttons to MembersView (Gherkin scenario 4)\n- Created `PollCard.vue` component with voting, percentages, animated bars (Gherkin scenario 7)\n- Added `FGPoll`, `FGPollVote` types + seed data + store functions\n- Added `FGBadge`, `FGBadgeAward`, energy points system (Gherkin scenario 8)\n- Added badges/achievements section to `MemberDetailView`\n- Added `createEvent()` store function + New Event modal to EventsView\n- Added all 12 doc files to DocsView index\n- Build passes: `✓ built in ~800ms`, all chunks emitted cleanly\n- App confirmed running and rendering in Edge browser with full Circle.so-style UI\n\n### In Progress\n- Verifying all Frappe ecosystem DocType mappings against real repos (research task completed, analysis pending)\n- Checking frappe/payments billing integration requirements\n- Performance investigation (dev server slow to respond, occasionally unresponsive)\n\n### Blocked\n- Dev server occasionally hangs/times out on `localhost:8080` (worked after restart)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Tailwind v4 requires `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin in `vite.config.ts` — was the root cause of completely unstyled page\n- React `.tsx` files deleted entirely (none imported by Vue components)\n- Poll/badge/gamification features added as in-store mock data matching Frappe patterns\n- Store uses pub/sub (`listeners` Set + `emit()`) for Vue reactivity — all mutations call `emit()`\n\n## Next Steps\n- Verify prototype type definitions against real Frappe DocType JSON fields from all 6 repos (gameplan, lms, raven, helpdesk, eps, payments)\n- Add `frappe/payments` billing/paywall types and UI (subscription plans, locked spaces, paywall screen per Gherkin scenario 5)\n- Ensure `GP Discussion.last_post_type` field supports `GP Poll` option (confirmed in real gameplan repo)\n- Ensure `GP Discussion.content` has `read_only` + `ignore_xss_filter` flags mapped correctly\n- Add `GP Reaction` as child table (istable) not separate DocType — real gameplan stores reactions as Table field on Discussion\n- Add `HD Ticket` safeguarding triage queue integration (helpdesk)\n- Add `Notification Log` for notification inbox (Frappe core)\n- Fix dev server reliability (check for memory/process issues)\n- Add toast notifications for mutation feedback across all views\n\n## Critical Context\n- Real Frappe gameplan `GP Discussion` stores reactions as a `Table` field (child table `GP Reaction`), NOT as separate linked records — prototype currently uses separate reaction records with `reference_doctype`/`reference_name`\n- Real Frappe gameplan has `last_post_type` (Select: GP Comment/GP Poll) + `last_post` (Dynamic Link) on discussions — prototype doesn't map these yet\n- `GP Comment` has no `title` field in real gameplan (prototype has one)\n- `GP Project` is a child of `GP Team` in real gameplan — prototype has `team` field but no members table\n- LMS `Course` has `upcoming` (Check) field not in prototype types\n- EPS uses `Energy Point Log` + `Energy Point Rule` + `Energy Point Request` (3 DocTypes) — prototype simplified to flat arrays\n- `frappe/payments` has `Subscription` DocType with `status` (Active/Cancelled/Past Due/Credit Hold) and `Subscription Plan Detail` child table — prototype has no paywall/billing UI yet\n- `Raven Channel` has `is_direct_message` (Check) field for DMs — prototype types use `type` field instead\n- `Raven Message` has `message_type` (Select: Text/JSON/HTML/Markdown) — prototype has no `message_type`\n- ONNX sentiment model loading is stub (`pass`) — keyword fallback always runs\n- `compute_embedding()` returns random vectors — not real embeddings\n- `vectors.py` uses PostgreSQL `ON CONFLICT` syntax — incompatible with MariaDB default\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\community-launchpad-proto\\` — project root\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\community-launchpad-proto-backup-pre-fix\\` — backup before changes\n- `package.json` — dependencies, removed lucide-react, renamed project\n- `vite.config.ts` — added `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin\n- `eslint.config.js` — Vue-only plugins (verified working)\n- `src/mock-data/types.ts` — all TypeScript interfaces mirroring Frappe DocTypes (+ added FGPoll, FGBadge, FGEnergyPoints)\n- `src/mock-data/store.ts` — reactive in-memory store with all mutations (+ added poll, badge, energy point functions)\n- `src/mock-data/seed.ts` — seeded fictional data (+ added polls, badges, energy points, poll votes)\n- `src/data/store.ts` — production API bridge wrapping mock store (+ added poll/badge exports)\n- `src/components/PollCard.vue` — NEW: poll voting UI with percentage bars\n- `src/components/PostCard.vue` — integrated PollCard\n- `src/views/MentorsView.vue` — added \"Message\" button on active match cards\n- `src/views/MembersView.vue` — added search/filter + action buttons\n- `src/views/EventsView.vue` — added \"New event\" modal + createEvent()\n- `src/views/MemberDetailView.vue` — added badges/achievements section\n- `src/views/DocsView.vue` — added all 12 doc file entries\n- `src/main.ts` — Vue Router 4 with 16 lazy-loaded routes\n- `src/styles.css` — Tailwind v4 config with design tokens\n- `docs/09_GHERKIN_UX_SCENARIOS.md` — 12 acceptance scenarios driving implementation\n- `docs/10_FRAPPE_UI_MIGRATION.md` — frappe-ui adoption guide\n- `docs/05_CIRCLE_TO_FRAPPE_MAPPING.md` — Circle.so → Frappe feature map\n- `docs/06_FRAPPE_ECOSYSTEM_TWIN.md` — app-by-app ecosystem breakdown\n- `docs/03_PORTING_GUIDE.md` — production porting steps\n- `fg_companion/api.py` — Python backend (rsvp, similar_discussions, toggle_reaction)\n- `fg_companion/ai/sentiment.py` — ONNX sentiment (stub, keyword fallback)\n- `fg_companion/ai/vectors.py` — pgvector embeddings (stub, random vectors)\n- `fg_companion/hooks.py` — Frappe lifecycle hooks",
      "timestamp": 1781948694624
    },
