aduates from UK universities and a variety of career fields.\n\nTogether, we host workshops, on-demand content, insightful panels, organise in-person events and offer mentoring.\n\nOur platform has become an unmatched resource and network for first-generation undergraduates, providing valuable knowledge and personal support.\n\nWe take a systems-change approach, by delivering corporate training and campaigns, designed to raise awareness and eliminate barriers in higher education.\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://firstgens.co.uk/social.jpg\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" imageSrcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Ff3q7nt2c%2Fproduction%2F5cd29543c7bd5fbfbc46068115eb2345dad51b92-6720x4480.jpg%3Frect%3D0%2C260%2C6720%2C3961%26w%3D1208%26h%3D712&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Ff3q7nt2c%2Fproduction%2F5cd29543c7bd5fbfbc46068115eb2345dad51b92-6720x4480.jpg%3Frect%3D0%2C260%2C6720%2C3961%26w%3D1208%26h%3D712&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Ff3q7nt2c%2Fproduction%2F5cd29543c7bd5fbfbc46068115eb2345dad51b92-6720x4480.jpg%3Frect%3D0%2C260%2C6720%2C3961%26w%3D1208%26h%3D712&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Ff3q7nt2c%2Fproduction%2F5cd29543c7bd5fbfbc46068115eb2345dad51b92-6720x4480.jpg%3Frect%3D0%2C260%2C6720%2C3961%26w%3D1208%26h%3D712&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Ff3q7nt2c%2Fproduction%2F5cd29543c7bd5fbfbc46068115eb2345dad51b92-6720x4480.jpg%3Frect%3D0%2C260%2C6720%2C3961%26w%3D1208%26h%3D712&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.sanity.io%2Fimages%2Ff3q7nt2c%2Fproduction%2F5cd29543c7bd5fbfbc46068115eb2345dad51b92-6720x4480.jpg%3Frect%3D0%2C260%2C6720%2C3961%26w%3D1208%26h%3D712&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_nex