      "type": "answer",
      "text": "## Goal\nBuild and deploy a production-ready FirstGens community platform — Vue 3 prototype mirroring Frappe DocTypes 1:1, now being ported to actual Frappe Framework (v15) running on WSL2 Ubuntu 24.04 with real Frappe ecosystem apps installed, FirstGens brand colors applied, and realistic seed data.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Production stack: Frappe Framework v15 + Gameplan + LMS + Helpdesk + Payments + fg_companion (custom app)\n- App should look like Circle.so (designed in Lovable, refactored to Vue 3)\n- In-memory mock store today for prototype; production bridge (`src/data/store.ts`) pre-wired with Frappe REST API endpoints\n- TypeScript types mirror real Frappe DocType field names 1:1\n- Brand colors from FirstGens (chabba.ai): `--green: #3e654a`, `--stone: #f6ede0`, `--burnt-maroon: #37272f`, `--clay: #d17147`, `--yellow: #ffba56`, `--khaki: #c1a167`, `--camel: #da9e5d`, `--blue: #8bc8d4`\n- Fonts: \"Right Grotesk Narrow\" / \"Right Grotesk\" (headings), \"Public Sans\" (body)\n- `--primary: var(--green)` (#3e654a), `--body-bg: var(--white)`, `--body-color: var(--black)`, `--border-radius: 1rem`\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Created backup at `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\community-launchpad-proto-backup-pre-fix`\n- Fixed `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin, cleaned React leftovers, ESLint verified\n- Added Poll, Badge, Energy Points, Mentoring, Events, DMs, Docs features\n- Fixed types to match real Frappe DocType fields (GPDiscussion, GPComment, LMSCourse, LMSLesson, LMSEnrollment, LMSCourseProgress, LMSCertificate, Raven Channel/Message, HDTicket, EPS, Subscription types)\n- Added frappe/payments billing types (FGSubscriptionPlan, FGSubscription, FGPaymentPlan)\n- Added frappe/helpdesk types (HDTicket, HDAgent, HDTeam)\n- Updated Raven Channel: `dm_user_1`/`dm_user_2` (was `member_a`/`member_b`), added `channel_type`, `is_direct_message`, `is_thread`, `is_self_message`, `workspace`\n- Updated Raven Message: `channel` (was `thread`), `text` (was `content`), added `message_type`, `file`, `image_width`, `image_height`\n- Updated GPDiscussion: added `last_post_type`, `last_post`, `pin_scope`\n- Updated GPComment: added `edited_at`\n- Updated LMSCourse: added `card_gradient`, `paid_certificate`, `published_on`, `upcoming`, `disable_self_learning`, `course_price`, `currency`, `amount_usd`, `instructors`, `rating`\n- Updated LMSEnrollment: added `member_name`, `member_username`, `role`, `current_lesson`, `payment`, `certificate`, `purchased_certificate`\n- Updated LMSCourseProgress: added `chapter`, `member_name`, `is_scorm_chapter`, status includes \"Partially Complete\"\n- Updated FGNotification: added `HD Ticket` to document_type union\n- Added seed data: tickets, subscription plans, payment plans\n- All store mutators/exports updated for new field names\n- Build passes: `✓ built in ~945ms`, 0 errors, 4 expected `v-html` warnings\n- **WSL2 Ubuntu 24.04 set up** with NOPASSWD sudo (`andiekobbie ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL`)\n- **System deps installed**: Python 3.12, Node.js 20, MariaDB 10.11, Redis, wkhtmltopdf, build-essential, cron\n- **Frappe bench v5.31 initialized** at `/home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench` (frappe-branch version-15)\n- **Site created**: `firstgens.localhost` (db_name: `_6aedce4afc2119b2`, admin password: `admin`)\n- **5 Frappe apps installed**: frappe 15.112.0, gameplan 0.0.1, lms 2.45.2, helpdesk 1.10.0, payments 0.0.1\n- **Site verified running**: HTTP 200 on `http://localhost:8000`\n- **MariaDB root password**: `admin123` (mysql_native_password auth)\n- Bench services running: Redis (ports 11000, 13000), Gunicorn (port 8000), Socket.IO (port 9000)\n\n### In Progress\n- Creating `fg_companion` Frappe app via `bench new-app` (interactive prompts require careful input piping — in progress)\n- Applying FirstGens brand theme (#3E654A primary, stone/stone backgrounds) across all apps\n- Seeding all apps with realistic personas and data\n\n### Blocked\n- Raven app clone keeps timing out (slow network) — not installed\n- Wiki app requires Python 3.14+ — incompatible with system Python 3.12, skipped\n- `bench new-app` is interactive — last attempt had mismatched prompt count for piped input\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Tailwind v4 requires `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin — was root cause of unstyled page\n- React `.tsx` files deleted entirely (none imported by Vue components)\n- Poll/badge/gamification features added as in-store mock data matching Frappe patterns\n- Store uses pub/sub (`listeners` Set + `emit()`) for Vue reactivity\n- **WSL2 over Docker** for production — leaner, no Docker Desktop license, Ubuntu already installed\n- **MariaDB root switched to `mysql_native_password`** auth (empty password initially, then set to `admin123`) because bench new-site couldn't connect with default unix_socket plugin\n- **Helpdesk v1.9.2** installed instead of latest (v1.22.2 requires Python 3.14+)\n- **Payments version-15 branch** installed instead of main (main requires Python 3.14+)\n- **fg_companion app to be created via `bench new-app --no-git`** with correct piped prompts\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Complete `fg_companion` app creation (fix piped input for bench new-app prompts: Title, Description, Publisher, Email, License=mit, Frappe version=version-15, then y/n)\n2. Install fg_companion app into site\n3. Create custom CSS theme file with FirstGens brand colors and apply via hooks.py\n4. Seed realistic personas across all apps (Gameplan discussions, LMS courses/enrollments, Helpdesk tickets, DM threads)\n5. Build assets with `bench build`\n6. Provide login credentials\n7. Optionally retry Raven install (network permitting)\n\n## Critical Context\n- **MariaDB root password is `admin123`** — needed for bench commands that require `--mariadb-root-password`\n- **Site DB name is randomized**: `_6aedce4afc2119b2` (not `firstgens`) — `bench new-site` generates random DB names\n- **Site config path**: `/home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench/sites/firstgens.localhost/site_config.json` — `db_password: 3bbDyn9w2N7Yvz6J`\n- Real Frappe gameplan `GP Discussion` stores reactions as a `Table` field (child table `GP Reaction`), NOT separate linked records\n- Real Frappe gameplan has `last_post_type` (Select: GP Comment/GP Poll) + `last_post` (Dynamic Link)\n- Real Frappe `Raven Channel` uses `dm_user_1`/`dm_user_2` for DMs, `channel_type` Select field\n- EPS uses `Energy Point Log` + `Energy Point Rule` + `Energy Point Request` (3 DocTypes)\n- `frappe/payments` has `Subscription` DocType with `Subscription Plan Detail` child table\n- **PowerShell mangling issue**: double quotes and backticks in `wsl -d Ubuntu -e bash -c \"...\"` get interpreted by PowerShell — always write scripts to files first, copy to WSL, then execute\n- `bench new-site` hangs if MariaDB root uses `unix_socket` plugin — must be `mysql_native_password`\n- `bench start` must be running before `bench migrate` or `bench build` will fail\n- `bench build` fails with `yarn run production` error — frontend assets don't build, but backend still works\n- **Bench commands must use full path** `/home/andiekobbie/.local/bin/bench` from PowerShell, or set `PATH=\"$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH\"` in bash scripts\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\community-launchpad-proto\\` — project root (Vue 3 prototype)\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\community-launchpad-proto-backup-pre-fix\\` — backup before changes\n- `src/mock-data/types.ts` — all TypeScript interfaces mirroring real Frappe DocTypes (updated: GPDiscussion, GPComment, LMSCourse, LMSChapter, LMSLesson, LMSEnrollment, LMSCourseProgress, LMSCertificate, FGDMThread, FGDMMessage, FGDMChannelMember, HDTicket, HDAgent, HDTeam, FGEnergyPointRule, FGEnergyPointLog, FGEnergyPointRequest, FGSubscriptionPlan, FGSubscription, FGSubscriptionPlanDetail, FGPaymentPlan, FGNotification)\n- `src/mock-data/store.ts` — reactive in-memory store with all mutations (updated: dm_user_1/dm_user_2, new LMS fields, ticket/subscription exports)\n- `src/mock-data/seed.ts` — seeded fictional data (updated: DM threads/messages with new fields, tickets, subscription plans, payment plans)\n- `src/data/store.ts` — production API bridge (updated: ticket/subscription exports)\n- `src/components/PollCard.vue` — poll voting UI\n- `src/views/MentorsView.vue` — mentor match with \"Message\" button\n- `src/views/MembersView.vue` — search/filter + action buttons\n- `src/views/EventsView.vue` — new event modal\n- `src/views/MemberDetailView.vue` — badges/achievements section\n- `/home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench/` — WSL2 Frappe bench root\n- `/home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench/sites/firstgens.localhost/` — Frappe site\n- `/home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench/sites/firstgens.localhost/site_config.json` — site DB config\n- `/home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench/apps/` — installed Frappe apps (frappe, gameplan, lms, helpdesk, payments)\n- FirstGens brand CSS vars extracted from `https://firstgens.co.uk/_next/static/css/ce5823380df76152.css`",
