      "type": "thought",
      "text": "Progress! Teams and projects were created. Several issues:\n\n1. Users fail because Redis isn't running (not critical for direct insertion)\n2. Discussions fail with \"cannot unpack non-iterable NoneType object\" - likely a field mismatch\n3. LMS courses need categories created first\n4. Helpdesk tickets need priorities and ticket types created first\n\nLet me fix these issues step by step. First, let me check what fields GP Discussion expects.",
