 error: Could not find Category: Academic Skills\nCourse error: Could not find Category: Career Development\n\n=== Creating HD Tickets ===\nTicket error: Could not find Priority: Medium\nTicket error: Could not find Priority: Low\nTicket error: Could not find Priority: Low\n\n=== PHASE 2 COMPLETE ===\n",
