      "type": "thought",
      "text": "OK, now I know the issues:\n\n1. `name` columns for GP Discussion and HD Ticket are auto-increment integers, not strings. I should use 0 or let them auto-increment.\n2. LMS Course doesn't have an `instructor` column at the top level - it's stored in the child table `Course Instructor`.\n\nLet me fix this.",
