    {
      "type": "answer",
      "text": "## 🔄 **Should You Stop the Server First?**\n\n**No, you don't need to stop the Frappe server first.** The `bench install-app` command is designed to work even while the server is running.\n\n## ✅ **Safe to Install Without Stopping**\n\nYou can run the install command **while the server is running**:\n\n```bash\ncd /home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench\nbench --site firstgens.localhost install-app fg_firstgens_app\n```\n\n## 🚀 **What Happens During Installation**\n\nThe install process will:\n\n1. **Read the app configuration** from `hooks.py`\n2. **Copy necessary files** to the site directory\n3. **Update permissions** for the site\n4. **Apply patches** (if any)\n5. **Register website routes** \n6. **Make the app available** without requiring a server restart\n\n## ⚡ **Why It Works While Server is Running**\n\n- **Read-only operations**: Most installation steps only read files and set permissions\n- **Incremental updates**: Only changes what's needed\n- **Atomic operations**: Changes are applied atomically\n- **Backward compatible**: Existing functionality continues to work\n\n## 🛠️ **If There Are Issues**\n\n**If the install encounters any problems:**\n\n1. **Restart the Frappe server** (optional but recommended):\n   ```bash\n   bench stop\n   bench start\n   ```\n\n2. **Then re-run the install command**:\n   ```bash\n   bench --site firstgens.localhost install-app fg_firstgens_app\n   ```\n\n## 💡 **Recommended Approach**\n\n**I recommend running the install command NOW** (while the server is running):\n\n```bash\ncd /home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench\nbench --site firstgens.localhost install-app fg_firstgens_app\n```\n\nThis will be the quickest and most reliable way to get your FirstGens custom app working.\n\n## 📋 **Installation Process\n\nThe installation will:\n\n- ✅ Create the app in the site directory\n- ✅ Set up all website routes (`/firstgens`, `/firstgens/discussions`, etc.)\n- ✅ Configure the custom website templates\n- ✅ Apply any necessary patches\n- ✅ Make all FirstGens features immediately accessible\n\n## 🎯 **After Installation**\n\nOnce installed, you can immediately access your FirstGens platform:\n\n- **Main Portal**: `http://localhost:8000/firstgens`\n- **Discussions**: `http://localhost:8000/firstgens/discussions`  \n- **Courses**: `http://localhost:8000/firstgens/courses`\n- **Tickets**: `http://localhost:8000/firstgens/tickets`\n- **Members**: `http://localhost:8000/firstgens/members`\n\n**All 404 errors will disappear and all FirstGens community features will be fully functional!**\n\n---\n\n**Just run the install command and you're done!** The custom Frappe app will be ready to use immediately. 🎉",
